org.xandercat.pmdb.controller

Class ImdbSearchController

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.xandercat.pmdb.controller.ImdbSearchController

  • @Controller
public class ImdbSearchController
extends Object
    Controller for functions involving IMDB search. This includes IMDB browsing, adding new movies using IMDB as the information source, and associating existing movie collection movies with movies on the IMDB.
    Author:
    Scott Arnold
